0.1.name: wordpress/target-page-navigation
0.1.description: This plugin adds a new optoin (only available on the Add/Edit page sections) that enables the author to assign the page to one of 4 navigation types(Super, Head, Side, Page, Foot) to be used in a new function (wp_list_navtype_pages), that will replace the wp_list_pages() function.
